attributes.title: Homemade walnut liquer
attributes.description:
Created on August 23, 2010 by lea55555 on Sourcemap.org:

A month ago, me and my mother decided to make homemade walnut liquer. We used the folloving ingredients: nuts, lemon, schnapps, sugar, vanilla sticks, thyme, balm and honey. These ingredients are from the folloving countries:
